WEBVTT

00:02.785 --> 00:04.352
- ♪ Hey, here comes Sunny
keeping it fun ♪

00:04.439 --> 00:05.962
♪ Never says never,
never gives up ♪

00:06.049 --> 00:07.746
♪ It's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:07.833 --> 00:09.487
♪ Hey ♪

00:09.574 --> 00:11.185
♪ Gear up and go
in the Glam Van ♪

00:11.272 --> 00:12.925
♪ Hair styling
with her best friends ♪

00:13.013 --> 00:15.928
♪ It's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:16.016 --> 00:19.062
♪ Oh, it's a Sunny Day ♪

00:19.149 --> 00:20.759
♪ She'll put a smile
on your face ♪

00:20.846 --> 00:23.284
- Whoo-hoo!

00:23.371 --> 00:27.984
- ♪ Sunny is shining
all the way ♪

00:28.071 --> 00:31.161
♪ Yeah, she's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:31.248 --> 00:33.381
♪ Having a sunny, sunny day ♪

00:33.468 --> 00:34.904
- Hoo-hoo!

00:36.036 --> 00:38.821
[upbeat music]

00:38.908 --> 00:44.479
♪ ♪

00:44.566 --> 00:45.871
- [barks]
- [giggles]

00:45.958 --> 00:47.960
Thanks, Rosie.
[hair spray hissing]

00:48.048 --> 00:49.919
- There.
What do you think?

00:50.006 --> 00:52.095
- [gasps]
Oh, I love it!

00:52.182 --> 00:54.271
- I'm so glad
you like it, Avery.

00:54.358 --> 00:57.970
- Thanks, Sunny.
Bye.

00:58.058 --> 00:59.581
[door bell jingles]

00:59.668 --> 01:02.366
- Oh.
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

01:02.453 --> 01:04.716
- [sighs]
- Whoa.

01:04.803 --> 01:06.370
- [grunts]

01:06.457 --> 01:09.330
Careful, Violet, or you'll--

01:09.417 --> 01:10.809
hmm.

01:10.896 --> 01:12.463
- [chitters]

01:12.550 --> 01:14.683
[laughs]
Ooh!

01:14.770 --> 01:16.293
- Cool!

01:16.380 --> 01:19.731
♪ ♪

01:19.818 --> 01:23.648
[machine beeps, whirrs]

01:23.735 --> 01:26.521
Hey, that turned out great...
[chuckles]

01:26.608 --> 01:28.392
Can you do that again, Violet?

01:28.479 --> 01:30.307
- Again, again!

01:30.394 --> 01:32.004
[laughter]

01:32.092 --> 01:34.659
- There.
There.

01:34.746 --> 01:36.096
Perfect.

01:36.183 --> 01:37.619
- Ooh!
- [giggles]

01:37.706 --> 01:39.664
Everything okay up there, Rox?

01:39.751 --> 01:42.928
[laughter]

01:43.015 --> 01:45.235
- Sure is.

01:45.322 --> 01:47.890
Look at the chalks
Violet and I made.

01:47.977 --> 01:50.501
- Nice!
- Those are great.

01:50.588 --> 01:51.937
[door bell jingles]
- Ooh.

01:52.024 --> 01:53.417
Sounds like we have a customer.

01:53.504 --> 01:55.419
- ♪ Hello! ♪

01:55.506 --> 01:57.291
- Not just any customer.

01:57.378 --> 02:00.076
Dame Tralada,
welcome to my salon.

02:00.163 --> 02:01.643
You're right on time.

02:01.730 --> 02:03.645
- ♪ Hello, Sunny ♪

02:03.732 --> 02:06.778
And...

02:06.865 --> 02:10.260
team.

02:10.347 --> 02:12.654
Oh, nice to see you!

02:12.741 --> 02:14.482
- How can we help you today?

02:14.569 --> 02:17.354
- I'm performing
my favorite opera,

02:17.441 --> 02:19.400
"The Birdie of Seville,"
tonight,

02:19.487 --> 02:23.447
and I simply must have a
hairstyle that looks the part,

02:23.534 --> 02:25.797
that says...

02:25.884 --> 02:28.017
- Bird?
- Exactly!

02:28.104 --> 02:31.412
- I know just the thing--
a bird wing flip!

02:31.499 --> 02:33.022
- [gasps]
Ooh, sounds...

02:33.109 --> 02:35.590
♪ Perfect ♪
- [yipping]

02:35.677 --> 02:37.853
- Don't worry, Her Majesty.

02:37.940 --> 02:39.637
I didn't forget you.

02:39.724 --> 02:43.163
Her Majesty is also
going to be a bird.

02:43.250 --> 02:47.732
She's the first dog ever to
play a major role in an opera.

02:47.819 --> 02:49.343
all: Ooh.

02:49.430 --> 02:50.779
- Way to go!

02:50.866 --> 02:52.737
- [gasps]
That's so exciting!

02:52.824 --> 02:55.479
- We can give Her Majesty
a bird wing flip too.

02:55.566 --> 02:57.177
- Marvelous.

02:57.264 --> 03:00.745
Just make sure Her Majesty's
style has some shine to it.

03:00.832 --> 03:04.271
You know how
Her Majesty loves shiny things.

03:04.358 --> 03:05.576
- Shiny!

03:05.663 --> 03:08.362
I love shiny!

03:08.449 --> 03:10.277
Ooh, shiny!

03:10.364 --> 03:12.104
[shampoos twinkling]

03:12.192 --> 03:13.889
[barks]

03:13.976 --> 03:15.282
- [chitters]
- [yelps]

03:15.369 --> 03:16.979
- [confused squeak]

03:17.066 --> 03:18.807
- Oh, no, you don't.

03:18.894 --> 03:22.767
- Um, maybe we should get
Her Majesty styled first.

03:22.854 --> 03:24.421
- Oh, my!

03:24.508 --> 03:27.381
I just realized
I forgot our costumes!

03:27.468 --> 03:29.644
How could I be so forgetful?

03:29.731 --> 03:33.735
You get started on Her Majesty
and I'll be back in a jiffy.

03:33.822 --> 03:35.737
- No problem.

03:35.824 --> 03:38.522
- I'll take her over to Lacey
and KC in the pet parlor.

03:38.609 --> 03:40.132
- Wait for me!

03:40.220 --> 03:43.571
- Bye, Queenie!
Hope you enjoyed your bath.

03:43.658 --> 03:45.137
- Oh, I did.

03:45.225 --> 03:48.402
It was a bath fit for a queen.

03:48.489 --> 03:49.838
- Bye, Lacey!
Thanks!

03:49.925 --> 03:51.274
- Thanks, KC.

03:51.361 --> 03:54.016
- And have a Lacey day!

03:54.103 --> 03:56.323
I've always wanted to say that.

03:56.410 --> 03:57.976
- Hello!
- Hi, Doodle.

03:58.063 --> 04:00.805
Hi, Blair.
Is this our next appointment?

04:00.892 --> 04:02.590
- Yup.
- Her Majesty needs a--

04:02.677 --> 04:04.244
- [barks]
- Oh.

04:04.331 --> 04:07.203
- [panting]
Ooh, shiny!

04:07.290 --> 04:09.379
[excited barking]
Whee!

04:09.466 --> 04:12.556
- A, uh, a bath, and a...

04:12.643 --> 04:14.341
[platform whirrs]
- Ooh...[barks]

04:14.428 --> 04:16.125
[panting]
Bows, glitter!

04:16.212 --> 04:17.996
So much to see!

04:18.083 --> 04:19.433
- [gasps]

04:19.520 --> 04:21.783
- And, uh, where was I?

04:21.870 --> 04:23.698
- Bath, blow-dry, fluff?

04:23.785 --> 04:25.787
Don't worry.
We can handle it.

04:25.874 --> 04:28.529
- Treats, treats, treats!
[chomps]

04:28.616 --> 04:31.706
[playful music]

04:31.793 --> 04:34.099
- Okay, then.
See you later. Have fun.

04:34.186 --> 04:37.102
- [barks]

04:37.189 --> 04:39.496
[barks]

04:39.583 --> 04:40.758
- Let's get her
on the groomer mats.

04:40.845 --> 04:42.194
- [barks]

04:42.282 --> 04:45.154
- We have to catch her first.

04:45.241 --> 04:48.549
[both barking]

04:50.768 --> 04:52.509
- [gasps]
- [barks]

04:52.596 --> 04:54.294
- [panting]

04:54.381 --> 04:56.078
[yelps]
[crash]

04:56.165 --> 04:58.907
- [barking]

04:58.994 --> 05:01.823
- Oh.

05:01.910 --> 05:04.608
Oh, gotcha!
- Good move.

05:04.695 --> 05:08.220
Now, hold her there
and I'll press the...

05:08.308 --> 05:10.310
- Shiny!

05:10.397 --> 05:11.746
- [yelps]
- Oh, no!

05:11.833 --> 05:13.182
Don't touch that button!

05:13.269 --> 05:15.402
- [hollers]

05:15.489 --> 05:17.099
Whoa!

05:17.186 --> 05:19.928
[screaming]

05:20.015 --> 05:21.321
Whoa!

05:21.408 --> 05:23.540
- [gasps]
Oh!

05:23.627 --> 05:25.586
Hey.
[buttons beeping]

05:25.673 --> 05:28.415
- [barks]

05:28.502 --> 05:31.156
- I don't want a bath!

05:31.243 --> 05:33.942
[groans]

05:34.029 --> 05:36.901
- [tiredly]
Washed, dried, and ready to go.

05:36.988 --> 05:38.599
- [barks]
- Thanks, Lacey.

05:38.686 --> 05:40.775
She looks great.

05:40.862 --> 05:42.777
You did a great job too, KC.

05:42.864 --> 05:45.736
- Thanks.

05:45.823 --> 05:48.435
- Why don't you guys
take a smoothie break?

05:48.522 --> 05:51.002
Looks like you could use one.

05:51.089 --> 05:55.224
- Yeah, a long smoothie break.

05:55.311 --> 05:57.487
- Okay, ready to style?

05:57.574 --> 06:01.056
- Let's do it!
- Yeah!

06:01.143 --> 06:03.058
- Who says dogs
can't have wings?

06:03.145 --> 06:04.581
[laughs]

06:04.668 --> 06:07.584
[bright music]

06:07.671 --> 06:09.107
♪ ♪

06:09.194 --> 06:11.762
- Some color for your feathers.

06:13.198 --> 06:15.462
- And braid them like so.

06:15.549 --> 06:16.898
- Glitter nails will make you

06:16.985 --> 06:19.117
stand out on stage,
Her Majesty.

06:19.204 --> 06:22.207
- Shiny!
I like!

06:22.294 --> 06:25.167
- A little hairspray
to hold it all in place.

06:25.254 --> 06:26.777
[hair spray hissing]

06:26.864 --> 06:28.692
- And the finishing touch...

06:28.779 --> 06:32.130
[dramatic music]

06:32.217 --> 06:34.176
Her costume!

06:34.263 --> 06:38.963
♪ ♪

06:39.050 --> 06:41.357
- All done.
What do you think?

06:41.444 --> 06:44.316
- ♪ I love it! ♪

06:44.404 --> 06:47.145
- ♪ Me too ♪

06:47.232 --> 06:48.582
[barks]

06:48.669 --> 06:50.932
- This is one
for the Style Files.

06:51.019 --> 06:52.760
- [gasps]
Shiny mirror!

06:52.847 --> 06:54.805
[shutter clicks]

06:54.892 --> 06:57.373
- [sighs]
Well, close enough.

06:57.460 --> 06:59.027
- [panting, barks]

06:59.114 --> 07:00.985
[laughter]

07:01.072 --> 07:03.466
- Okay,
Dame Tralada, your turn.

07:03.553 --> 07:05.120
[Violet and Rosie chittering]

07:05.207 --> 07:08.340
- Make sure you use the
Very Merry Berry shampoo.

07:08.428 --> 07:10.212
It's my favorite.

07:10.299 --> 07:11.996
The smell of it always

07:12.083 --> 07:15.217
makes me feel fabulous.

07:15.304 --> 07:17.741
- Who doesn't love the smell
of Very Merry Berry,

07:17.828 --> 07:19.482
or even the name?

07:19.569 --> 07:22.180
It's just so...very merry!

07:22.267 --> 07:24.922
- You should make everything
with that scent--

07:25.009 --> 07:28.012
soap, perfume, conditioner.

07:28.099 --> 07:31.015
- I wish I could,
but the berries are so rare,

07:31.102 --> 07:33.365
there are barely enough
to make the shampoo.

07:33.453 --> 07:36.630
In fact, we only have
one bottle left.

07:36.717 --> 07:39.459
But that's more than enough
to shampoo your hair.

07:39.546 --> 07:42.374
[Violet and Rosie chittering]

07:42.462 --> 07:45.203
- Yeah!
[laughs]

07:45.290 --> 07:46.640
- [barks]
- [barks]

07:46.727 --> 07:48.642
Oh.

07:48.729 --> 07:50.948
Ooh, shiny.

07:51.035 --> 07:54.386
[barks]
[laughter]

07:54.474 --> 07:57.128
- Give way!
- [barks]

07:57.215 --> 08:00.480
- Her Majesty,
get down from there!

08:01.785 --> 08:03.700
- Yikes!
- [gasps]

08:03.787 --> 08:05.310
[tense music]

08:05.397 --> 08:07.443
- [gasps]

08:07.530 --> 08:08.923
- Oh!
- Oh, no!

08:09.010 --> 08:12.100
Whoa!

08:12.187 --> 08:14.276
Oh, no.

08:14.363 --> 08:16.496
- Oh, my special

08:16.583 --> 08:18.672
Very Merry Berry shampoo.

08:18.759 --> 08:21.326
Is it...
- It's all gone.

08:21.413 --> 08:23.720
- Oh!

08:27.158 --> 08:29.726
- The last bottle of
my very favorite shampoo,

08:29.813 --> 08:31.423
down the drain.

08:31.511 --> 08:34.383
- We have lots of other
great shampoos.

08:34.470 --> 08:37.038
- Yeah, most of them
are on the floor now,

08:37.125 --> 08:39.388
but that makes it easier to,

08:39.475 --> 08:41.738
um, pick one out?

08:41.825 --> 08:45.133
- No!
It has to be Very Merry Berry.

08:45.220 --> 08:48.963
It's the only shampoo
I ever use before a big show.

08:49.050 --> 08:52.314
- Well, I'll just have
to go get some berries

08:52.401 --> 08:53.707
and make more shampoo.

08:53.794 --> 08:57.319
- Oh, wonderful.
When do we leave?

08:57.406 --> 08:59.103
- Um, "we"?

08:59.190 --> 09:00.757
- Of course!

09:00.844 --> 09:03.107
The shampoo is very
important to me.

09:03.194 --> 09:04.848
- Are you sure?

09:04.935 --> 09:07.764
Very Merry Berries
only grow at the very top

09:07.851 --> 09:10.158
of the highest peak
in Friendly Falls.

09:10.245 --> 09:12.595
- Which means
you'd have to climb up there.

09:12.682 --> 09:14.466
- No.
I'm going with Sunny.

09:14.554 --> 09:17.252
- [barks]
Me too!

09:17.339 --> 09:19.820
- And I have just the thing
to help in the search--

09:19.907 --> 09:22.257
my opera glasses!
See?

09:22.344 --> 09:25.173
With these, I'll be able
to spot a Very Merry Berry

09:25.260 --> 09:27.567
from a mile away.

09:27.654 --> 09:29.569
- Hey, I'm up for an adventure.

09:29.656 --> 09:31.919
- We'd better get started
if we wanna be back in time

09:32.006 --> 09:33.747
for your big
performance tonight.

09:33.834 --> 09:36.880
- Rox and I will stay here
and keep an eye on things.

09:36.967 --> 09:38.969
- [barks]
All of us.

09:39.056 --> 09:40.449
- [chuckles]
Yeah.

09:40.536 --> 09:42.364
- Thanks, everybody.

09:42.451 --> 09:44.758
Ready, set...

09:44.845 --> 09:46.934
all: Gear up and go!

09:47.021 --> 09:50.198
[bright music]

09:50.285 --> 09:53.680
♪ ♪

09:53.767 --> 09:55.682
[engine revving]

09:55.769 --> 10:01.470
♪ ♪

10:01.557 --> 10:03.167
- Whoo-hoo!

10:03.254 --> 10:05.648
- [giggles]

10:05.735 --> 10:08.695
[dragonfly wings humming]

10:10.087 --> 10:14.701
- [inhales] Ah,
the fresh mountain air.

10:14.788 --> 10:17.834
It smells so...mountain-y!

10:17.921 --> 10:24.928
♪ ♪

10:25.363 --> 10:26.843
- I'll lead the way.

10:26.930 --> 10:28.932
An expert adventurer like me

10:29.019 --> 10:31.587
knows everything
about the woods.

10:31.674 --> 10:33.241
[both scream]

10:33.328 --> 10:35.373
- [chitters]
- Oh, ah, I, uh...

10:35.460 --> 10:37.637
[clears throat]
I mean, um,

10:37.724 --> 10:39.769
that was a squirrel.

10:39.856 --> 10:41.336
Any other questions?

10:41.423 --> 10:43.077
- [giggles]

10:43.164 --> 10:45.296
Maybe I better
lead the way, Doodle.

10:47.081 --> 10:49.779
- [caws]

10:51.738 --> 10:54.262
Mmm!

10:54.349 --> 10:59.093
- Hmm, that bird
looks familiar, doesn't it?

10:59.180 --> 11:00.964
- [caws]

11:01.051 --> 11:03.053
- It looks just like
Her Majesty--

11:03.140 --> 11:07.623
wings, colors,
exactly the same.

11:07.710 --> 11:10.321
- [squeaks]
- Hmm.

11:10.408 --> 11:14.021
- Amazing.
I love the outdoors.

11:14.108 --> 11:16.371
You never know
what you're gonna find.

11:16.458 --> 11:19.853
- [groans]
All I can find are

11:19.940 --> 11:22.551
things to step over and--

11:22.638 --> 11:24.466
oof, run into.

11:24.553 --> 11:25.902
[hollers]

11:25.989 --> 11:27.643
[groans, sighs]

11:27.730 --> 11:31.386
Is nature always
this difficult?

11:31.473 --> 11:34.824
- [giggles]
Once you learn to enjoy it,

11:34.911 --> 11:37.131
you'll never wanna
be inside again.

11:37.218 --> 11:41.396
[upbeat country rock music]

11:41.483 --> 11:45.269
♪ The next time that you're
wondering where I'm off to ♪

11:45.356 --> 11:48.751
♪ I'll say the wild
was calling out to me ♪

11:48.838 --> 11:52.407
♪ And once you know the
great outdoors like I do ♪

11:52.494 --> 11:55.323
♪ You'll never wonder
where I'm gonna be ♪

11:55.410 --> 11:56.716
[giggles]

11:56.803 --> 11:58.282
- ♪ So don't look for me
at the movies ♪

11:58.369 --> 12:00.154
- ♪ Don't look for me
at the mall ♪

12:00.241 --> 12:02.373
- ♪ If you don't see
the open sky ♪

12:02.460 --> 12:03.897
[together]
♪ Don't look for me at all ♪

12:03.984 --> 12:05.768
♪ Outside, outside ♪

12:05.855 --> 12:08.075
♪ I'm gonna be outside ♪

12:08.162 --> 12:09.598
♪ Outside, outside ♪
- [squeaks]

12:09.685 --> 12:11.818
[together]
♪ I'm gonna be outside ♪

12:11.905 --> 12:15.560
- ♪ If you think nature
should be celebrated ♪

12:15.647 --> 12:17.867
♪ Where birds and trees
and flowers can be found ♪

12:17.954 --> 12:19.477
- Ooh.

12:19.564 --> 12:21.871
- ♪ If you think staying clean
is overrated ♪

12:21.958 --> 12:23.568
Oh, yeah.

12:23.655 --> 12:25.875
- ♪ Then pack a bag, come on,
we're nature bound ♪

12:25.962 --> 12:27.311
- Yeah!
[laughs]

12:27.398 --> 12:29.226
♪ So don't look for us
at the movies ♪

12:29.313 --> 12:31.185
- ♪ Don't look for us
at the mall ♪

12:31.272 --> 12:32.839
- ♪ If you don't see
the open sky ♪

12:32.926 --> 12:35.102
♪ Don't look for us at all ♪

12:35.189 --> 12:36.581
[together]
♪ Outside, outside ♪

12:36.668 --> 12:38.583
- [vocalizing]
- ♪ We're gonna be outside ♪

12:38.670 --> 12:40.411
[together]
♪ Outside, outside ♪

12:40.498 --> 12:42.196
♪ We're gonna be outside ♪

12:42.283 --> 12:44.851
- Whoo!
- [laughs]

12:44.938 --> 12:48.376
[mellow music]

12:48.463 --> 12:51.640
- [sighs] We're never gonna
get all this cleaned up.

12:51.727 --> 12:53.642
both: Never say never.

12:53.729 --> 12:55.905
[laughter]

12:55.992 --> 12:57.864
- [chuckles, sniffs]

12:57.951 --> 12:59.082
- All those different shampoos

12:59.169 --> 13:01.171
do smell good,
don't they, Violet?

13:01.258 --> 13:03.043
- Yeah.
- [sniffs]

13:03.130 --> 13:04.784
Orange...
[sniffs]

13:04.871 --> 13:06.437
Raspberry.

13:06.524 --> 13:08.396
All of them!

13:08.483 --> 13:09.527
[laughter]

13:09.614 --> 13:11.051
- [sniffs]

13:11.138 --> 13:14.010
Hey, that gives me an idea.

13:15.620 --> 13:19.494
- Hmm, the berries
have to be nearby.

13:19.581 --> 13:21.191
- [barks]
Shiny!

13:21.278 --> 13:23.237
Shiny!

13:23.324 --> 13:25.413
- Found them--
Very Merry Berries.

13:25.500 --> 13:27.371
We're done here.
You're welcome.

13:27.458 --> 13:30.810
- Sorry, Doodle.
Those are raspberries.

13:30.897 --> 13:33.551
- Hmm.
Aha!

13:33.638 --> 13:35.031
What about these?

13:35.118 --> 13:37.294
- Those are blueberries.

13:37.381 --> 13:38.948
- [groans]

13:39.035 --> 13:41.081
As an expert adventurer,
I should know this,

13:41.168 --> 13:43.692
but what exactly
are we looking for?

13:43.779 --> 13:45.128
- Very Merry Berries are

13:45.215 --> 13:47.609
yellow, bright,
and shiny with--

13:47.696 --> 13:49.045
- Green and pink spots?

13:49.132 --> 13:50.699
- Yes.
How did you know?

13:50.786 --> 13:53.441
- [gasps] Because
that bird is eating some!

13:53.528 --> 13:55.008
[heavenly music]

13:55.095 --> 13:56.748
- [chomps]

13:56.836 --> 13:59.273
[squeaks, caws loudly]

13:59.360 --> 14:01.449
- The Very Merry Berries
must be close.

14:01.536 --> 14:02.972
Let's go!

14:04.713 --> 14:06.889
- [chitters]

14:06.976 --> 14:08.586
- Hmm?

14:08.673 --> 14:10.893
- [soft chittering]

14:10.980 --> 14:12.939
- [confused yip]

14:14.505 --> 14:17.378
[yips]

14:17.465 --> 14:20.424
- Rosie and Violet smelling
all those different shampoos

14:20.511 --> 14:22.209
gave me an idea.

14:22.296 --> 14:24.211
If we put the
right ones together,

14:24.298 --> 14:26.256
we can make it smell
just like...

14:26.343 --> 14:28.258
- Very Merry Berries!

14:28.345 --> 14:31.261
- Right, then we could
make our own shampoo--

14:31.348 --> 14:33.089
- And the Dame would love it!

14:33.176 --> 14:34.525
- Yay!
- Yeah!

14:34.612 --> 14:36.049
Okay.

14:37.964 --> 14:39.704
[both ooh]

14:39.791 --> 14:43.056
Tell me if any of these
smell like a Very Merry Berry.

14:43.143 --> 14:45.058
Close your eyes and sniff.

14:45.145 --> 14:47.495
- [sniffs]
Too sweet.

14:47.582 --> 14:49.410
- How's this?
- [sniffs]

14:49.497 --> 14:51.151
Too sour.

14:51.238 --> 14:52.979
Hmm...
[sniffs]

14:53.066 --> 14:55.633
Too much like an old sock.

14:55.720 --> 14:57.809
Wait, an old sock?

14:57.897 --> 15:00.029
[Violet and Rosie laugh]

15:00.116 --> 15:01.988
- Very funny, guys.

15:02.075 --> 15:03.815
[laughter]

15:03.903 --> 15:06.862
[mellow music]

15:06.949 --> 15:08.559
- We made it.

15:08.646 --> 15:09.996
- [sniffs, gasps]

15:10.083 --> 15:12.737
I-I think I smell it.

15:12.824 --> 15:15.697
[gasps]
Yes, Very Merry Berry!

15:15.784 --> 15:17.742
- [sniffs]
Me too.

15:17.829 --> 15:20.180
Can I borrow those?

15:20.267 --> 15:23.313
♪ ♪

15:23.400 --> 15:26.403
That's it--
a Very Merry Berry!

15:28.666 --> 15:30.538
- [gasps]
There's only one left.

15:30.625 --> 15:32.670
- That's okay.

15:32.757 --> 15:35.673
The smell is so strong, we only
need one to make your shampoo.

15:35.760 --> 15:37.110
[all inhaling]

15:37.197 --> 15:39.068
[together]
Ahh.

15:39.155 --> 15:41.462
- There's nothing else like it.

15:41.549 --> 15:43.420
- Be berry,
berry careful with that...

15:43.507 --> 15:44.595
[giggles]

15:44.682 --> 15:47.294
- Don't worry, Doodle.
I will.

15:47.381 --> 15:50.340
Now, let's get back
to the salon.

15:50.427 --> 15:51.951
- [caws]

15:52.038 --> 15:54.605
- Hmm?
[barks]

15:54.692 --> 15:58.435
- Her Majesty?

15:58.522 --> 16:00.307
- If we hurry,
we'll still have time

16:00.394 --> 16:01.743
to make the shampoo
before your show.

16:01.830 --> 16:02.874
- Hurry, hurry!

16:02.962 --> 16:04.876
- [caws]
- [gasps] Duck!

16:04.964 --> 16:06.008
- [caws]
- [barks]

16:06.095 --> 16:07.792
[squeaks]

16:07.879 --> 16:11.100
Whee!
[giggles]

16:11.187 --> 16:14.190
- Oh, no!
- Oh, my baby!

16:16.453 --> 16:19.326
[dramatic music]

16:19.413 --> 16:22.894
- [pants]
No sign of them anywhere.

16:22.982 --> 16:24.505
- Which way should we go?

16:24.592 --> 16:27.769
- Oh, that bird
has my sweet dog.

16:27.856 --> 16:29.727
I'll never get her back.

16:29.814 --> 16:31.164
- Never say never.

16:31.251 --> 16:33.122
Opera glasses, please.

16:37.257 --> 16:39.215
There she is.

16:39.302 --> 16:42.392
The bird must think
Her Majesty is her baby.

16:42.479 --> 16:45.004
- Right, because
their styles are the same.

16:45.091 --> 16:48.181
- Oh,
thank goodness she's fine.

16:48.268 --> 16:50.313
- But how are we going
to get her back?

16:50.400 --> 16:52.054
- You two distract the bird.

16:52.141 --> 16:55.840
I'll figure out a way to
climb up and get Her Majesty.

16:55.927 --> 16:57.407
I'll need some ribbon

16:57.494 --> 16:59.888
and an extra sturdy hair clip.

16:59.975 --> 17:02.586
[bright music]

17:02.673 --> 17:08.766
♪ ♪

17:08.853 --> 17:10.290
[grunts]

17:12.988 --> 17:15.382
- Look, I'm a big baby bird!

17:15.469 --> 17:17.645
[caws]

17:17.732 --> 17:19.995
Come play with me!

17:20.082 --> 17:22.824
- [trills softly]

17:22.911 --> 17:25.087
- [cawing]

17:25.174 --> 17:27.394
That's all I got.

17:27.481 --> 17:29.222
- Let me try, Doodle.

17:29.309 --> 17:32.094
No one can resist my voice.

17:32.181 --> 17:35.184
[vocalizes]

17:36.229 --> 17:38.231
- [barks]

17:38.318 --> 17:40.146
- [squawks softly]
- Uh...

17:40.233 --> 17:42.757
Hm.
Everyone's a critic.

17:42.844 --> 17:45.368
- Sorry, Sunny.
It's not working.

17:45.455 --> 17:47.892
Too bad I don't have
green or pink spots

17:47.979 --> 17:49.416
like a Very Merry Berry,

17:49.503 --> 17:53.028
then that bird would
notice me for sure.

17:53.115 --> 17:54.508
- Doodle, that's it!

17:54.595 --> 17:57.076
That's how we'll
tempt the bird out of her nest.

17:57.163 --> 17:59.730
- You're going to give me
green and pink spots?

17:59.817 --> 18:01.471
- No.

18:01.558 --> 18:04.170
We're going to
give the bird this.

18:04.257 --> 18:06.215
- The last berry?

18:06.302 --> 18:07.825
But what about the shampoo?

18:07.912 --> 18:09.958
- Huh, shampoo?

18:10.045 --> 18:12.830
What's shampoo compared to
my best friend in the world?

18:12.917 --> 18:14.441
- Aww.

18:14.528 --> 18:16.051
Remind me to give
everybody a big hug

18:16.138 --> 18:18.097
once we get Her Majesty back.

18:18.184 --> 18:20.577
- Okay, here goes.

18:20.664 --> 18:24.190
I just have to make sure
the bird sees it.

18:24.277 --> 18:25.930
Hey, bird, fetch!

18:26.017 --> 18:28.933
[grunts]
- [squawks]

18:29.020 --> 18:30.848
[caws loudly]

18:30.935 --> 18:31.980
- It worked!
[gasps]

18:32.067 --> 18:33.677
Hurry!

18:33.764 --> 18:36.506
- [grunting]

18:38.682 --> 18:39.727
Gotcha!

18:39.814 --> 18:41.294
- Hi.

18:41.381 --> 18:42.991
Whee!
- [gasps]

18:43.078 --> 18:46.037
Oh, my precious!
[smooches]

18:46.125 --> 18:48.475
You're safe!
- [barks]

18:48.562 --> 18:51.652
- Okay, hugs for everybody!

18:51.739 --> 18:53.088
[barks]

18:53.175 --> 18:54.785
- [laughs]

18:54.872 --> 18:57.440
We better get back to
the salon, Dame Tralada.

18:57.527 --> 18:58.746
Your show's going
to start soon

18:58.833 --> 19:00.530
and we still need
to style your hair

19:00.617 --> 19:02.924
and get you into your costume.

19:03.011 --> 19:05.100
- Then let's go!

19:05.187 --> 19:08.756
[curious music]

19:08.843 --> 19:11.976
- [curious squeak]

19:12.063 --> 19:14.805
[excited squawk]

19:14.892 --> 19:18.592
[upbeat music]

19:18.679 --> 19:20.898
[door bell jingles]
- We're back!

19:20.985 --> 19:22.335
- Hey, Sunny.

19:22.422 --> 19:24.424
- There you are.
- Berries?

19:24.511 --> 19:26.165
- We had to leave
the berry behind.

19:26.252 --> 19:28.167
It's a long story.

19:28.254 --> 19:29.646
- A bird took Her Majesty

19:29.733 --> 19:32.388
and we had to trade the berry
to get her back.

19:32.475 --> 19:35.174
- Okay, maybe it's not so long.

19:35.261 --> 19:38.568
I'm sorry we can't make your
favorite shampoo, Dame Tralada,

19:38.655 --> 19:41.005
but maybe we can
come up with something

19:41.092 --> 19:42.181
you'll like just as much.

19:42.268 --> 19:44.835
- Maybe something like this?

19:44.922 --> 19:46.272
[both sniff]

19:46.359 --> 19:48.839
- But that smells just like...

19:48.926 --> 19:50.493
- Very Merry Berry!

19:50.580 --> 19:52.930
I don't believe it.
How did you...

19:53.017 --> 19:54.889
- It was Rox's idea.

19:54.976 --> 19:58.022
We combined lots of
different shampoos together.

19:58.109 --> 20:00.199
- Wow!
Thanks, Rox.

20:00.286 --> 20:02.549
Thanks, Blair.
Great work.

20:02.636 --> 20:05.204
What do you say, Dame Tralada?
Wanna try it out?

20:05.291 --> 20:07.206
- I say it's...

20:07.293 --> 20:09.904
♪ wonderful! ♪

20:09.991 --> 20:15.736
♪ ♪

20:15.823 --> 20:17.172
- Mmm.

20:17.259 --> 20:19.522
- Mmm-mmm-mmm.
- [barks]

20:19.609 --> 20:21.394
- When we're finished,

20:21.481 --> 20:24.266
you and Dame Tralada
will look exactly alike!

20:24.353 --> 20:28.314
♪ ♪

20:28.401 --> 20:30.229
- Ooh.
- [yips]

20:32.056 --> 20:34.015
- Here.

20:34.102 --> 20:37.279
- Ooh, shiny.

20:37.366 --> 20:39.760
- Violet, that's so nice.

20:39.847 --> 20:40.978
Here, Her Majesty.

20:41.065 --> 20:43.764
I'll put it on for you.
- [barks]

20:43.851 --> 20:45.418
- Ta-da!

20:45.505 --> 20:47.637
[dogs barking]
- Wow, yeah!

20:49.552 --> 20:51.511
- ♪ I l-l-l-l-love it! ♪

20:51.598 --> 20:54.644
[shutter clicks]
And as a thank you,

20:54.731 --> 20:58.474
you must all come to see
"The Birdie of Seville,"

20:58.561 --> 21:01.999
though I'm afraid the only
seats left are way in the back.

21:02.086 --> 21:03.740
- No problem.

21:03.827 --> 21:06.526
We'll have a bird's-eye view
with these.

21:08.136 --> 21:10.791
- [operatic singing]

21:10.878 --> 21:13.968
[bright classical
music playing]

21:14.055 --> 21:16.971
[crowd cheering]

21:17.058 --> 21:20.279
♪ ♪

21:20.366 --> 21:23.194
- Whoa, better put those
opera glasses away, Sunny.

21:23.282 --> 21:25.066
- Why, Doodle?

21:25.153 --> 21:27.024
- ♪ La, la, la, la, la ♪

21:27.111 --> 21:29.288
- Ooh, shiny.

21:29.375 --> 21:31.768
- [sighs]
That's why.

21:31.855 --> 21:32.900
[laughter]

21:32.987 --> 21:35.903
- [vocalizing]

21:35.990 --> 21:39.298
♪ ♪

21:39.385 --> 21:40.516
[cheers and applause]

21:42.213 --> 21:43.824
- Hi, it's me, Sunny,

21:43.911 --> 21:46.522
with another look
inside the Style Files.

21:46.609 --> 21:50.309
Wow, look at
that feathery flip!

21:50.396 --> 21:54.008
For this hairstyle and more,
check out the Nick Jr. App.

21:54.095 --> 21:57.359
[bright music]

21:57.446 --> 21:59.796
Keep smiling.
Keep styling.

21:59.883 --> 22:04.061
[laughs]

22:04.148 --> 22:11.112
♪ ♪
